notesStmt.note: Title listed by Poleman and New Catalogus Catalogorum is Ṛgvedapadapāṭha.
Written 10-13 lines per leaf. ff.3-8 accented in red. Lacks beginning and end.

Aṣṭaka 1 (ff. 3-73): lacks beginning. Begins: meghaṁ. juṣanta vahnayaḥ. pāvakā. naḥ sarasvatī. vājebhiḥ. vājinī'vatī. yajñaṁ. vaṣṭu. dhiyā'vasuḥ. codayitrī. Colophon: Iti prathamāṣṭake aṣṭamodhyāyah. Śrīsāmbāryaṇam astu. Idaṁ pustakaṁ Nārāyaṅa Bhaṭṭanene [sic.] iti upanāmakena likhitam. Svārthaṁ parārthaṁ. Śake 1758 plavanāma samvatsare mārgaśīṣaśuddha 3 ravi vāre samāsah. Yādṛśaṁ pustakaṁ dr̥ṣṭvā tādṛśaṁ likhitaṁ mayā. Yadi śuddham aśuddhaṁ vā mama doṣo na vidyate. Tailād raksej[j]alād rakse[c]chitilavandhanāt. Mūrkhahastena dātavyaṁ evaṁ vadati pustakaṁ.

Aṣṭaka 2 (69 leaves) colophon: iti āśvalāyanaśākalapadāyāṁ dvitīyāṣṭaka samāptaḥ... Bhagnapr̥ṣṭikarigrivastabdhadr̥ṣtir adhomukhaṃ. kasṭena likhitaṁ granthaṃ yatnena paripālayet. Nārāyaṅa Bhaṭaneneyena [sic.] likhitaṃ.

Aṣṭaka 3 colophon: iti aśvalāyanapadāyāṁ tr̥tīyāṣṭake aṣṭamodhyāyaḥ. śrī sāmba. bhagnapr̥ṣṭikaṭigrivastabdhadr̥ṣṭir adhomukhaṁ. Kaṣṭena likhitaṁ granthaṁ yatnena paripālayet. Śake 1759 kilakanāma samvatsare caitraśuddha 15 guruvāsare tr̥tīṣṭakasamāptaṁ. yādṛṣaṁ pustakaṁ dr̥ṣṭvā tādṛṣaṁ likhitaṁ mayā. Yadi śuddham aśuddham vā mama doṣo na vidyate.
Aṣṭaka 4 lacks ending. Ends: divaḥ'dāsasya. sat'patiḥ. saḥ. hi. viśvā. ati. pārthivā. rayiṁ. dāśat. mahi'tvanā. va...
